      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is in the oven, boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>giant couscous</strong> to a pot with 500ml<span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\"> [650ml] </span>[800ml]</span> <strong>boiling water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 5-7 min or until tender with a slight bite, then drain and rinse briefly under <strong>cold running water</strong> to remove any excess starch</p><p>Set aside for later</p>",
