    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]<strong> </span>boiled water </strong>and mix to combine</p>",
