    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has had an initial 20 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>cooked giant couscous</strong></p><p>Pour the <strong>chicken stock </strong>over the top and return the tray[s] to the oven for 5 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>honey-harissa chicken breast & courgette tray bake</strong></p>",
